[[美國消費品安全委員會|美國消費品安全委員會]]在一篇新聞稿中提出「沒有完美的兒童安全包裝，因此不要用安全包裝作為保護兒童的第一道防線。相反的，需要將包裝（包括兒童安全包裝）視為保護兒童的最後一道防線」<ref>{{cite press release|title=New National Emergency Hotline Assessed; CPSC Joins in Launching Poison Prevention Week to Stop 30 Deaths Each Year|publisher=CPSC|url=http://www.cpsc.gov/Trans/ppw02.html|accessdate=26 March 2009|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081212003244/http://www.cpsc.gov/trans/ppw02.html|archivedate=2008年12月12日}}</ref>

==背景==
可以鎖住蓋子的兒童安全包裝是在1967年由{{le|亨利·布勞爾特|Henri Breault}}發明<ref name=cnd>{{cite web|url=http://www.cdnmedhall.org/dr-henri-j-breault|title=Dr. Henri Breault|publisher=Canadian Medical Hall of Fame|accessdate=28 February 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120307180213/http://www.cdnmedhall.org/dr-henri-j-breault|archivedate=2012年3月7日}}</ref>。

由於許多因兒童打開家中物品，誤食內容物造成的意外，使得美国国会通過了由猶他州議員{{le|法蘭克·莫斯|Frank E. Moss}}提出的{{le|1970年防毒包装法案|Poison Prevention Packaging Act of 1970}}。這也授權[[美國消費品安全委員會|美國消費品安全委員會]]<ref>{{cite web
 |author1     = CPSC
 |title       = Poison Prevention Packaging Information
 |publisher   = U.S. Consumer Product Safety Commission
 |date        = February 9, 2007
 |url         = http://www.cpsc.gov/BUSINFO/pppainfo.html
 |accessdate  = 19 December 2008
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20081219131131/http://www.cpsc.gov/businfo/pppainfo.html
 |archivedate = 2008年12月19日
}}</ref><ref name="Viscusi1995">{{cite book|last=Viscusi|first=W. Kip|title=Fatal tradeoffs: public and private responsibilities for risk|url=http://books.google.com/?id=uBRYXzjOztcC&pg=PA235&dq=%22safety+cap%22medicine|accessdate=6 November 2010|year=1995|publisher=Oxford University Press US|isbn=978-0-19-510293-2|page=235}}</ref>可以在此領域訂定相關規定。這幾十年來已將此延伸到這其他的有害物質，包括[[美国国家环境保护局|美国国家环境保护局]]管制的化學物質。也正在協調提昇有關的[[國際標準|國際標準]]。

==兒童安全包裝的問題==
對於一些年長者或是行動不便的人士而言，可能會無法開啟有兒童安全包裝的物品<ref>{{cite web|last=de la Fuente|first=Javier|title=The use of a universal design methodology for developing child-resistant drug packaging|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/220012972_The_use_of_a_universal_design_methodology_for_developing_child-resistant_drug_packaging?ev=prf_pub|work=Master's Thesis|publisher=Michigan State University|accessdate=2013-10-16|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304063557/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/220012972_The_Use_of_a_Universal_Design_Methodology_for_Developing_Child-resistant_Drug_Packaging?ev=prf_pub|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=de la Fuente|first=Javier|title=Perceptions and attitudes of people with disabilities and older adults about child-resistant drug packaging|url=http://www.patientcompliancemedia.com/jpc/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Pages-from-JPC-Volume2-Issue2-21.pdf|work=Journal for Patient Compliance|accessdate=2013-10-16|author2=Bix, Laura|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131017001116/http://www.patientcompliancemedia.com/jpc/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Pages-from-JPC-Volume2-Issue2-21.pdf|archivedate=2013-10-17}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=de la Fuente|first=Javier|title=User-pack interaction: Insights for Designing Inclusive Child-resistant Packaging|url=http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-1-84996-166-0_9|work=Designing Inclusive Interactions|publisher=Springer Link|accessdate=2013-12-16|author2=Bix, Laura|pages=89–100|archive-date=2018-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615202854/https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007%2F978-1-84996-166-0_9|dead-url=no}}</ref>法令有要求相關測試需加以驗證，確認大部份的成年人可以正常使用<ref>{{cite web
  | author1 = CPSC
  | title = Testing procedure for special packaging
  | publisher = U.S. Consumer Product Safety Commission
  | url = http://www.ecfr.gov/cgi-bin/text-idx?SID=2187b921d122b7f6c3236f82ab235f2d&mc=true&node=se16.2.1700_120&rgn=div8
  | accessdate = 21 August 2015
  | archive-date = 2021-05-06
  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210506110226/https://www.ecfr.gov/cgi-bin/text-idx?SID=da4ffeecf0f7fce3da8dad1d28dd1d34&mc=true&node=se16.2.1700_120&rgn=div8
  | dead-url = no
  }}。</ref>。若家中沒有小孩的話，一些司法管轄區允藥劑師提供沒有兒童安全包裝的藥品。

